<body>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Local Computer Help You Can Trust</h1>
      <p>Serving Pittsburgh homes and small businesses with fast, honest, and affordable tech support.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mt-3">Request a House Call</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Services I Offer</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="card p-4">
            <h5>Computer Repair & Optimization</h5>
            <p>Speed up slow machines, remove viruses, fix startup problems, and clean out junk files.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="card p-4">
            <h5>Windows Reinstall & Upgrades</h5>
            <p>Clean installs of Windows 10/11, driver updates, and full system refreshes to bring machines back to life.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="card p-4">
            <h5>Data Backup & Recovery</h5>
            <p>Recover files from failed or damaged drives. Set up regular backup plans so you never lose your data again.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="card p-4">
            <h5>Printer Setup & Troubleshooting</h5>
            <p>Fix printer connection problems, install new printers, or set up print sharing in your home or small office.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="card p-4">
            <h5>Pickup, Repair & Return</h5>
            <p>Can’t wait while I work? I’ll take the device, fix it off-site, and return it ready to go — usually same or next day.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="card p-4">
            <h5>Website Help</h5>
            <p>Fix broken sites, help update content, or get you started with a simple website that actually works.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="why-me bg-secondary bg-opacity-10">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4">Why Choose McGrew Media?</h2>
      <p class="fs-5">I’m not a big box tech. I don’t upsell. I don’t waste your time. I’m local, experienced, and care about getting it right the first time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Need Help Right Now?</h2>
      <p class="mb-4 fs-5">Call or message me for same-day availability.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get In Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2025 McGrew Media – Serving Pittsburgh and surrounding areas</p>
      <p><a href="/contact" class="link-light text-decoration-none">Request Support</a></p>
    </div>
  </footer>

